#: app/templates/docs/cl_inbox.html:3
msgid "Mail from cr"
msgstr "crからのメール"

#: app/templates/docs/cl_inbox.html:5
msgid ""
"Every ctr has to icons in the navigation bar to see the mail from/to cr. "
"In mail from cr the default view will show only the pendings notes. To "
"see all notes click in see All"
msgstr "CR からのメールまたは CR へのメールを表示するには、すべての Ctr がナビゲーション バーにアイコンを表示する必要があります。 "

#: app/templates/docs/cl_inbox.html:11
msgid "Mark note as read"
msgstr "メモを既読としてマークする"

#: app/templates/docs/cl_inbox.html:13
msgid ""
"Every user can keep track of the notes he has read. New notes will appear"
" in bold letters. After reading the note you can mark it as read using "
"the icon of the envelope."
msgstr "すべてのユーザーは、自分が読んだメモを追跡できます。"

#: app/templates/docs/cl_inbox.html:21
msgid ""
"The new notes will appear as pending note. When the cl has finish with a "
"note (because it was answer, the information was trasmits, ...) you can "
"mark the note as done using the icon with an x as in the video. You can "
"mark the note again as pending clicking again."
msgstr "新しいノートは保留中のノートとして表示されます。 "

#: app/templates/docs/cl_inbox.html:27
msgid "Comments in a note for the cl"
msgstr "clのノートのコメント"

#: app/templates/docs/cl_inbox.html:29
msgid ""
"The cl can add some comments to the notes from cr (for example to see who"
" is going to take care of it) using the icon of the pencil. Only the cl "
"can see those comments"
msgstr "cl は、鉛筆のアイコンを使用して、cr からのメモにいくつかのコメントを追加できます (たとえば、誰がそれを処理するかを確認するため)。 "

#: app/templates/docs/cl_outbox.html:3
msgid "New mail to cr"
msgstr "crへの新着メール"

#: app/templates/docs/cl_outbox.html:5
msgid ""
"To create new mail for cr go to the page with the notes to cr and click "
"in New. Then use the pencil to edit the content of the note in english "
"(you can also add content in jp in the line \"content JP\"). It is "
"important to fill the references of the note. They will use the form \"cr"
" num/year\" or \"ctr num/year\""
msgstr "cr 用の新しいメールを作成するには、cr へのメモが記載されたページに移動し、[新規] をクリックします。"

#: app/templates/docs/cl_outbox.html:11
msgid "Add synology note to Sake"
msgstr "Sakeにsynologyノートを追加"

#: app/templates/docs/cl_outbox.html:13
msgid ""
"Now you can click in the folder icon to open the Synology folder link to "
"the note in Sake. Put/Create there all the files you want to send to cr. "
"Then in Sake click in the update icon to add all the files in the folder "
"to the note."
msgstr "これで、フォルダー アイコンをクリックして、Sake のノートへの Synology フォルダー リンクを開くことができます。 "

#: app/templates/docs/cl_outbox.html:19
msgid "Send the note to cr"
msgstr "メモを cr に送信する"

#: app/templates/docs/cl_outbox.html:21
msgid ""
"When everything is ready click in the send icon. A gray tick will appear."
" When the gray tick becomes blue means cr is already working with the "
"note"
msgstr "すべての準備ができたら、送信アイコンをクリックします。"

#: app/templates/docs/cr.html:3
msgid "How to navigate the registers and use the filter"
msgstr "レジスタを操作してフィルタを使用する方法"

#: app/templates/docs/cr.html:4
msgid "Introduction to matters"
msgstr "事項の紹介"

#: app/templates/docs/cr.html:5
