msgstr "事柄を使った完全な例"

#: app/templates/docs/cr_old.html:6
msgid "Register cr"
msgstr "crを登録する"

#: app/templates/docs/cr_old.html:8
msgid ""
"To see how to use Sake for cr first see all the pages for cl. It is the "
"same."
msgstr "cr酒の使い方を見るには、まずclの全ページを見てください。"

#: app/templates/docs/cr_old.html:9
msgid ""
"To see the different register click in the icon and choose the register "
"as in the next video."
msgstr "別のレジスタを表示するには、次のビデオのようにアイコンをクリックしてレジスタを選択します。"

#: app/templates/docs/cr_old.html:15
msgid "My notes"
msgstr "私のメモ"

#: app/templates/docs/cr_old.html:17
msgid ""
"To see all the notes I am involved click in pendings as in the video. "
"There are all the notes from cg,asr,ctr or r that have been assigne to me"
" and all the notes I have prepare to be send to cg,asr,ctr,r. We can "
"choose to see all the notes or only the pendings."
msgstr "私が関与しているすべてのメモを表示するには、ビデオのように保留中をクリックします。"

#: app/templates/docs/cr_old.html:23
msgid "Special registers"
msgstr "特殊レジスタ"

#: app/templates/docs/cr_old.html:25
msgid ""
"There are some special register you may have access. In the next video "
"you can see the register for cc. The special registers are: vc, vcr, dg, "
"cc, desr."
msgstr "アクセスできる特殊なレジスタがいくつかあります。"

